    "id": "nce2-018-he-often-does-this",
    "title": "Lesson 18: He Often does This",
    "audioFilename": "18－He Often does This.mp3",
    "duration": 69.146,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.21,
      "end": 1.63,
      "text": "Lesson 18.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第18课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 2.31,
      "end": 4.05,
      "text": "He often does this.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他经常干这种事。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 5.25,
      "end": 8.51,
      "text": "First listen and then answer the question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 9.59,
      "end": 12.11,
      "text": "What had happened to the writer's bag?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "作者的包出了什么事？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 14.31,
      "end": 20.05,
      "text": "After I had had lunch at a village pub, I looked for my bag.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我在一家乡村小酒馆吃过午饭后，开始寻找我的包。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 20.93,
      "end": 26.11,
      "text": "I had left it on a chair beside the door, and now it wasn't there.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我原来把它放在门边的椅子上，可现在不见了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 27.35,
      "end": 31.21,
      "text": "As I was looking for it, the landlord came in.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我正在寻找时，店主走了进来。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 31.99,
      "end": 34.25,
      "text": "Did you have a good meal?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“饭吃得好吗？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 34.75,
      "end": 35.29,
      "text": "he asked.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他问道。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 36.09,
      "end": 38.31,
      "text": "Yes, thank you, I answered.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“很好，谢谢。”我回答。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 39.05,
      "end": 40.77,
      "text": "But I can't pay the bill.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“但我没法付账。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 41.41,
      "end": 43.19,
      "text": "I haven't got my bag.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我的包不见了。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 43.99,
      "end": 47.99,
      "text": "The landlord smiled and immediately went out.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "店主笑了笑，立刻走了出去。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 48.69,
      "end": 54.07,
      "text": "In a few minutes, he returned with my bag and gave it back to me.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "几分钟后，他拿着我的包回来，把它还给了我。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 54.89,
      "end": 57.37,
      "text": "I'm very sorry, he said.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“非常抱歉，”他说。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 57.37,
      "end": 61.17,
      "text": "My dog had taken it into the garden.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“我的狗把它叼到花园里去了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 61.93,
      "end": 63.39,
      "text": "He often does this.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "它经常干这种事。”"
      }
    }
  ]
}
